body: I'm thinking, usually the data of  attribute info is small, can we open an interface that directly pass the serialized AttributeProto protobuf to the user? Then it will support any data type ONNX needs. I believe in most of the cases the performance of parsing an AttributeProto isn't a concern.
@snnn open an interface to get attribute info is more important, but now customer op can only get attributes for single data, some time it's not working
